Package cloud.filibuster.exceptions.filibuster.FilibusterGrpcTestRuntimeException

  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    FilibusterGrpcAmbiguousFailureHandlingException
    FilibusterGrpcAmbiguousFailureHandlingException indicates that the compositional verification failed due to ambiguous failure handling.
    FilibusterGrpcAmbiguousThrowAndErrorPropagationException
    FilibusterGrpcAmbiguousThrowAndErrorPropagationException is invoked when the test indicates both throw and error propagation: too ambiguous.
    FilibusterGrpcAssertionsDidNotHoldUnderErrorResponseException
    FilibusterGrpcAssertionsDidNotHoldUnderErrorResponseException is invoked when the assertions do not hold under error response of a specific status code.
    FilibusterGrpcAssertionsForAssertOnExceptionFailedException
    FilibusterGrpcAssertionsForAssertOnExceptionFailedException is invoked when assertions for assertOnException fail for a specific status code.
    FilibusterGrpcAssertionUsedOutsideFailureBlockException
    FilibusterGrpcAssertionUsedOutsideFailureBlockException is thrown when an assertion is used outside failureBlock(...).
    FilibusterGrpcAssertOnFaultException
    FilibusterGrpcAssertOnFaultException is invoked when the assertions in assertOnFault(...) fail.
    FilibusterGrpcAssertTestBlockFailedException
    FilibusterGrpcAssertTestBlockFailedException is invoked when assertions in assertTestBlock fail.
    FilibusterGrpcFailedRPCException
    FilibusterGrpcFailedRPCException is invoked when a failed RPC results in exception, but error codes and descriptions do not match.
    FilibusterGrpcInjectedFaultHasUnspecifiedFailureBehaviorException
    FilibusterGrpcInjectedFaultHasUnspecifiedFailureBehaviorException is invoked when a test injects a fault, but no specification of failure behavior is present.
    FilibusterGrpcInvokedRPCUnimplementedException
    FilibusterGrpcInvokedRPCUnimplementedException is thrown when an invoked RPCs was left UNIMPLEMENTED.
    FilibusterGrpcMissingAssertionForStatusCodeException
    FilibusterGrpcMissingAssertionForStatusCodeException is thrown when assertion block for a specific status code response is missing.
    FilibusterGrpcMultipleFaultsInjectedException
    FilibusterGrpcMultipleFaultsInjectedException is thrown when assertions in assertTestBlock fail due to multiple faults being injected.
    FilibusterGrpcReadOnlyRPCUsedOutsideAssertOnExceptionAndAssertOnFaultException
    FilibusterGrpcReadOnlyRPCUsedOutsideAssertOnExceptionAndAssertOnFaultException is thrown when readOnlyRPC is used outside assertOnException(...) and assertOnFault(...) block.
    FilibusterGrpcSideEffectingRPCUsedOutsideAssertOnExceptionAndAssertOnFaultException
    FilibusterGrpcSideEffectingRPCUsedOutsideAssertOnExceptionAndAssertOnFaultException is thrown when sideEffectingRPC is used outside assertOnException(...) and assertOnFault(...) block.
    FilibusterGrpcStubbedRPCHasNoAssertionsException
    FilibusterGrpcStubbedRPCHasNoAssertionsException is thrown when stubbed RPC has no assertions on invocation count.
    FilibusterGrpcStubForUsedOutsideStubBlockException
    FilibusterGrpcStubForUsedOutsideStubBlockException is thrown when stubFor is used outside stubBlock(...).
    FilibusterGrpcSuppressedStatusCodeException
    FilibusterGrpcSuppressedStatusCodeException is thrown when injected fault's status code was suppressed, but test indicates this should propagate directly upstream.
    FilibusterGrpcTestRuntimeException
    FilibusterGrpcTestRuntimeException is the abstract superclass of the exceptions that can be thrown from the GRPC test interface.
    FilibusterGrpcThrownExceptionHasUnspecifiedFailureBehaviorException
    FilibusterGrpcThrownExceptionHasUnspecifiedFailureBehaviorException is invoked when test throws an exception, but no specification of failure behavior is present.
    FilibusterGrpcVerifyThatUsedOutsideAssertStubException
    FilibusterGrpcVerifyThatUsedOutsideAssertStubException is thrown when verifyThat is used outside assertStubBlock(...).
